  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1995230/extras/62b1d3cdbbb8ca15d81bea25f3e534fd.avif?t=1725007234\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br>What Kind of game is chaotic loop? is this the right game for you? Let's find out!<br><br>Chaotic Loop is a little game, where your objective is complete the level you choose , also everytime you play something in the game will change (you could find different object to use, or maybe a particual quest will happen, or maybe a different boss will appear) and this makes the loop of finishing the level chaotic.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1995230/extras/10256f17b3e3ed34f5410c1e8c70cd47.poster.avif?t=1725007234\" width=600 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1995230/extras/10256f17b3e3ed34f5410c1e8c70cd47.webm?t=1725007234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1995230/extras/10256f17b3e3ed34f5410c1e8c70cd47.mp4?t=1725007234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>3 different characters each one with a special ability and a skin!<br>-Jenna: she can kick the enemies<br>-Droy: he can make a fireball fall from the sky<br>-Bino: makes a large shock wave that damages enemies and removes bullets from the screen<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1995230/extras/e27c57a94430ed53b0bed7e0a46ce773.avif?t=1725007234\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br>5 different maps to explore! City, Forest, Beach, Desert, And iceland! Each one with different type of platforms<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1995230/extras/e7937f9047d6813139adad7873d14eed.avif?t=1725007234\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br>16 different object to use, like a music stereo, cookies, and different type of guns!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1995230/extras/652ddd9154fbdb2f182282338060c9a4.avif?t=1725007234\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br> challanges, some little bosses, and more<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1995230/extras/90d77ac809b18aafdb8c7af58cc89615.avif?t=1725007234\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br>And different robots to fight with!",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1995230/extras/62b1d3cdbbb8ca15d81bea25f3e534fd.avif?t=1725007234\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br>What Kind of game is chaotic loop? is this the right game for you? Let's find out!<br><br>Chaotic Loop is a little game, where your objective is complete the level you choose , also everytime you play something in the game will change (you could find different object to use, or maybe a particual quest will happen, or maybe a different boss will appear) and this makes the loop of finishing the level chaotic.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1995230/extras/10256f17b3e3ed34f5410c1e8c70cd47.poster.avif?t=1725007234\" width=600 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1995230/extras/10256f17b3e3ed34f5410c1e8c70cd47.webm?t=1725007234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1995230/extras/10256f17b3e3ed34f5410c1e8c70cd47.mp4?t=1725007234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>3 different characters each one with a special ability and a skin!<br>-Jenna: she can kick the enemies<br>-Droy: he can make a fireball fall from the sky<br>-Bino: makes a large shock wave that damages enemies and removes bullets from the screen<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1995230/extras/e27c57a94430ed53b0bed7e0a46ce773.avif?t=1725007234\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br>5 different maps to explore! City, Forest, Beach, Desert, And iceland! Each one with different type of platforms<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1995230/extras/e7937f9047d6813139adad7873d14eed.avif?t=1725007234\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br>16 different object to use, like a music stereo, cookies, and different type of guns!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1995230/extras/652ddd9154fbdb2f182282338060c9a4.avif?t=1725007234\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br> challanges, some little bosses, and more<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1995230/extras/90d77ac809b18aafdb8c7af58cc89615.avif?t=1725007234\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br>And different robots to fight with!",
